rows.label: bf06140110_0030
rows.name:
it seems an official summit is to be
held between Superbia and Invidia.

rows.label: bf06140110_0040
rows.name:
A summit? You mean, about the
recent punch-up? But I thought...

rows.label: bf06140110_0050
rows.name:
Didn't His Holiness get them
to stop and sort it all out?

rows.label: bf06140110_0060
rows.name:
Perhaps there are some discussions they
would prefer Acedia not to be privy to.

rows.label: bf06140110_0070
rows.name:
Besides, Invidia doesn't like to associate
too closely with Acedia.

rows.label: bf06140110_0080
rows.name:
They'd hate to be seen as
acquiescing to the Pope's will.

rows.label: bf06140110_0090
rows.name: Gotta keep up appearances, you know?

rows.label: bf06140110_0110
rows.name: Like, letting him tell 'em what's what.

rows.label: bf06140110_0120
rows.name:
Hah, for such a spanner you sure use
some big words. How come?

rows.label: bf06140110_0130
rows.name: Stop calling me that! Buzz off, kitty-no-mates!

rows.label: bf06140110_0140
rows.name:
Anyway, this summit would explain
why Meleph isn't around...

rows.label: bf06140110_0150
rows.name:
Indeed.
She has much to attend to.
